WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.304 --> 00:00:01.966
If there is an increase in usage

2
00:00:01.966 --> 00:00:04.755
that has not been communicated to staff,

3
00:00:04.755 --> 00:00:07.846
they may not provide enough supplies to the area.

4
00:00:07.846 --> 00:00:10.776
For instance, if a unit has increased their use

5
00:00:10.776 --> 00:00:13.376
of large adult diapers but this is not noticed

6
00:00:13.376 --> 00:00:16.355
by the supply staff, then they unit may end up

7
00:00:16.355 --> 00:00:19.406
with fewer items than they desperately need.

8
00:00:19.406 --> 00:00:22.406
Good SCM helps to balance the trade-offs

9
00:00:22.406 --> 00:00:25.907
of fulfilling customer demands as efficiently as possible.

